         not representable in the character encoding being used for output (US-ASCII);
         not affected by character maps

Test XHTML output with cdata-section-elements that have (non-ASCII) characters
         not representable in the character encoding being used for output (US-ASCII);
         but unicode normalized (NFD)

Test XHTML output with cdata-section-elements that have (non-ASCII) characters
         not representable in the character encoding being used for output (US-ASCII);
         but unicode normalized (NFC)

Show that merging of output declarations is done after expanding the QNames in
        @name. (use two declarations with the same local name but different prefixes bound to one
        and the same namespace)
